### FRED 2 Open (FRED2 Open) executable selection

**Compatibility note**: Although FRED executable selection is supported on all platforms, FRED is currently available on Windows only.

**Note**: FRED launching is not enabled by default. To enable it, close wxLauncher if it's open, then open the file (on Windows) %AppData%\\wxlauncher\\global.ini in a text editor and add the following two lines to the end of the file:

	[opt]
	configfred=1

The equivalent file on Linux is ~/.wxlauncher/global.ini and on OS X is /Users/[YourUsername]/Library/Application Support/wxlauncher/global.ini .]

